      <title>中国正在采取一切措施拯救遭受重创的股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/everything-china-s-doing-to-rescue-its-battered-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自农历新年假期结束以来，中国股市一直难以获得牵引力，这加大了北京方面的压力，要求其提供更多支持，并恢复人们对正在努力应对房地产低迷和顽固通缩的经济的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/everything-china-s-doing-to-rescue-its-battered-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 06:23:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
